##############################################################
# Copyright (c) 2010-2014 VMware, Inc.  All rights reserved.
##############################################################
#
# English translation catalog.
#
# Please follow a few guidelines when editing this file:
#   . Try to maintain formatting (e.g., indentation and line breaks).
